      <title>特朗普团队考虑任命凯尔·巴斯担任财政部或国防职务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/trump-team-considering-kyle-bass-for-a-treasury-or-defense-role</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，特朗普政府正在考虑任命对冲基金资深人士、对华鹰派凯尔巴斯 (Kyle Bass) 担任财政部或国防部的职务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/trump-team-considering-kyle-bass-for-a-treasury-or-defense-role</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 16:57:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>秘鲁犯罪率飙升与跨国犯罪团伙猖獗有关</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/peru-sees-crime-surge-tied-to-transnational-gangs-roiling-region</link>
      <description><![CDATA[秘鲁正面临近年来最严重的公共安全危机，政府高层官员将混乱和暴力事件归咎于跨国犯罪组织，而邻国厄瓜多尔和哥伦比亚也陷入了混乱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/peru-sees-crime-surge-tied-to-transnational-gangs-roiling-region</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 16:48:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国将在 2025 年预算中向高收入者筹集 20 亿欧元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/france-to-raise-2-billion-from-high-earners-in-2025-budget</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据法国财政部官员称，法国政府预计，为应对富豪们的税收优化，今年将征收 20 亿欧元（21 亿美元）的税款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/france-to-raise-2-billion-from-high-earners-in-2025-budget</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 16:24:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普在达沃斯呼吁降低油价、降低利率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/trump-urges-opec-to-lower-oil-prices-warns-of-tariffs-at-davos</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普周四在达沃斯向世界各国领导人发表讲话时表示，他将要求沙特阿拉伯和其他石油输出国组织国家“降低石油成本”，并重申他将利用关税将制造业带回美国的威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/trump-urges-opec-to-lower-oil-prices-warns-of-tariffs-at-davos</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 16:16:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞士财政部长称欧洲经济衰退令瑞士担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/europe-s-economic-slump-has-swiss-worried-finance-chief-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士财政部长担心欧盟和德国的经济衰退也会打击瑞士企业，因为这两个国家都是瑞士最重要的贸易伙伴。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/europe-s-economic-slump-has-swiss-worried-finance-chief-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 16:03:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>保加利亚因通胀未达标而推迟采用欧元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/bulgaria-tempers-euro-adoption-push-on-inflation-criterion-miss</link>
      <description><![CDATA[保加利亚新成立的政府将推迟采取采用欧元的下一步措施，直到这个巴尔干国家正式满足欧盟要求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/bulgaria-tempers-euro-adoption-push-on-inflation-criterion-miss</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 14:33:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非总统签署土地征用法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/south-african-president-signs-off-on-land-expropriation-law</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非总统西里尔·拉马福萨同意一项新法律，该法律使国家可以更容易地为了公共利益征用土地，但必须支付公平的补偿。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/south-african-president-signs-off-on-land-expropriation-law</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 14:10:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普经济风险下马丁重返爱尔兰总理</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/ireland-s-martin-returns-as-prime-minister-for-second-term</link>
      <description><![CDATA[爱尔兰共和党领袖迈克尔·马丁 (Micheal Martin) 在去年 11 月的选举中当选为总理，主要现任执政联盟伙伴重新执政。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/ireland-s-martin-returns-as-prime-minister-for-second-term</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 13:47:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的农业选择表明她将尊重所有燃料来源</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/trump-s-agriculture-pick-set-for-senate-hot-seat-over-biofuels</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统提名的美国农业监管人曾经是一个团体的负责人，而该团体是美国最受欢迎的农产品——生物燃料的最强烈反对者之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/trump-s-agriculture-pick-set-for-senate-hot-seat-over-biofuels</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普关注运河问题 卢比奥将首次出访巴拿马</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/marco-rubio-plans-to-visit-panama-as-trump-eyes-canal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国务卿马尔科·卢比奥计划于下周晚些时候开始访问拉丁美洲，并访问巴拿马，凸显了唐纳德·特朗普总统收回巴拿马运河的认真态度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/marco-rubio-plans-to-visit-panama-as-trump-eyes-canal</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 02:11:26 GMT</pubDate>
